COMPANY OVERVIEW
REALLYGREATSITE.COM 
PAGE 03
Established on 9 July 1999, Focus Electrical Malaysia
Sdn. Bhd. is a leading distributor and supplier of high-
quality electrical and electronic equipment in Malaysia.
The company’s primary business activity is the trading
and distribution of electrical and electronic goods,
including 
lighting 
products 
and 
accessories.
Headquartered in Kuantan, Pahang, the company has
steadily expanded its operations with multiple branches
across the country, including Kuala Lumpur and
Terengganu.
With over two decades of experience, Focus Electrical
Malaysia has built a strong reputation for reliability,
product quality, and customer-oriented service. The
company is an authorized distributor for internationally
recognized brands such as Panasonic, Schneider
Electric, Osram, Hager, ABB, Bosch, Mega Kabel, DNF
Cable, Ecosparks, Joven, MK, SJ Lite, Selamat, PNE,
Taian Jaya, Tonn Cable, Maxguard, and many others.
3

FOCUS ELECTRICAL MALAYSIA
Our Vision
To be Malaysia’s leading and most trusted electrical and electronics
supplier, delivering innovative, high-quality products and exceptional
service to every home, business, and project across the nation.
Our Mission
To provide genuine, reliable, and competitively priced electrical and
electronic products from reputable brands.
To ensure every customer receives knowledgeable, friendly, and
efficient service at all our branches.
To support contractors, developers, and government projects with
tailored supply solutions and timely delivery.
To continuously improve our product range and services by
embracing innovation and sustainable practices.
To build lasting relationships with customers, partners, and the
community through integrity and commitment
4

Focus Electrical Malaysia
Solution
1) Leadership:
Leading by example
A better version of us inspires innovation and adaptability to
stay ahead of market trends.
Inspiring others to reach their full potential through
empowering employees.
2) Responsibility
Take ownership and accountability of our actions and
decisions.
Make positive impacts through responsible conduct of
ourselves.
Prioritises safety, ensuring the well-being of our employees
and customers.
3) Teamwork
An individual can run fast, but we can travel further as a team!
Promote open communication, trust and a collective shared
sense of mission and vision.
As a team, we can overcome any challenges and drive our
business to a whole new height.
Let’s celebrate every achievement of teams and individuals.
Core Values
5

Focus Electrical Malaysia
Behind Our Logo 
The Colour (Red)
Energy & Power: Red is a powerful colour often
associated 
with 
energy, 
strength, 
and
dynamism, perfect for a company in the
electrical and electronics sector where energy
flow and power are key.
Passion & Commitment: Red signals passion
and 
dedication, 
reflecting 
Focus 
Electrical
Malaysia commitment to providing quality
products and excellent service.
Visibility & Attention: Red grabs attention easily,
helping the logo stand out and be memorable in
a competitive market. It suggests urgency and
responsiveness, traits valued by customers who
want quick solutions.
The Logo Design
Concentric Circles: The multiple circles radiating
outward 
symbolize 
electrical 
waves 
or 
signals,
conveying the idea of energy transmission, connectivity,
and reach. This represents how Focus Electrical serves
a wide area across Malaysia with electrical products
and services.
Diagonal Line: The sharp diagonal line cutting through
the circles adds a sense of movement, direction, and
progress, implying that the company is forward-looking
and dynamic. It also gives the logo a feeling of precision
and sharp focus.
Bold “FOCUS” Text: The strong, bold lettering of
“FOCUS” reinforces the brand’s identity as reliable and
confident. The way the letters overlap slightly with the
circles suggests integration of the brand with the
electrical energy concept.

ACO GROUP BERHAD
ACO Group Berhad is a leading investment holding company
listed on the ACE Market of Bursa Malaysia. Specializing in the
distribution of electrical products, accessories, and related
solutions, the Group supply a diverse range of products to
various 
sectors, 
including 
construction, 
manufacturing,
commercial projects, and the oil & gas sector.
Through its network of subsidiaries and associate companies,
ACO Group maintains a strong presence in Malaysia, ensuring
the 
supply 
of 
high-quality 
products 
from 
reputable
international brands. Focus Electrical Malaysia Sdn. Bhd. forms
part of this network, enhancing the Group’s market coverage
in Pahang, Kuala Lumpur, and Terengganu.

“Dear Partners and Clients,
Welcome to Focus Electrical Malaysia Sdn. Bhd. As a trusted supplier of
electrical and electronic products, we are committed to delivering reliable
and innovative solutions that support your business needs. With strong
partnerships and a dedicated team, we aim to provide you with lasting
value and dependable service. At Focus Electrical, we believe our
success grows together with yours. Thank you for choosing us as your
partner. Together, let’s create opportunities and achieve success.”
Director’s Profile
MR ONG TEIK LEONG
Mr. Ong Teik Leong is the Director of
Focus 
Electrical 
Malaysia. 
He
graduated 
with 
a 
Bachelor 
of
Engineering in Electrical & Electronics
Engineering from the University of
Lincolnshire & Humberside, United
Kingdom. With his background in
engineering, he leads the company
with focus on quality, trust, and
customer satisfaction.
Under his guidance, Focus Electrical
Malaysia has continued to grow as a
reliable supplier of electrical and
electronic 
products 
while 
also
developing its own OEM brand to
serve wider market needs.
